The,getBible,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,Bible,verses,for,their,websites,in,the,version,and,translation,that,they,want,If,no,version,is,specified,the,English,language,King,James,Version,of,the,Bible,is,used,by,default,Some,of,the,other,languages,available,include,French,German,Hebrew,Greek,Afrikaans,Finnish,Swahili,Arabic,and,Esperanto